dBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T01:38:30.000Z","msg":"上次如果是但揾條友選主席 佢去主持, 已經唔駛搞到咁..."},{"pid":"dc3f5f3bf024b1aa7d0fe7f181b0ee893bb40fb1","tid":1135960,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T01:38:51.000Z","msg":"據知民主派主張今次會議進入選主席程序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915293b762e8ae469b74e8800b9df5580141d37f","tid":1135960,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5585171513dd2562c23898400404498c374230e2","tid":1135960,"uid":18772,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T01:36:41.000Z","msg":"就算打龍通都要交戲既<br />\n反派都要有反派既風範"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T01:39:30.000Z","msg":"郭垃圾, 醬爆何:佢係巴塞出黎"},{"pid":"65c66aa6169b8fdd1e16efb9412e9afc8287e1d5","tid":1135960,"uid":111372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:00:08.000Z","msg":"民主派主張今次會議進入選主席程序<br />\n又係邊D ON9/二五仔?"},{"pid":"19bc721c029aec4d8514e5ab6a9e2a91e12e7acc","tid":1135960,"uid":148332,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"01fceccf796cd20d1852c0e6bb64e02574881ed9","tid":1135960,"uid":145230,"like":5,"dislike":82,"score":-77,"quote":{"pid":"4af8d1b35ba8dac952e64c867ff1e7c1155dd555","tid":1135960,"uid":89931,"like":315,"dislike":1,"score":314,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T16:25:47.000Z","msg":"梁耀忠垃圾仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T16:48:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:43:36.000Z","msg":"算啦每個人都有睇錯既時侯...當年大把人覺得689好過唐英年"},{"pid":"263a691014b08907a3c88608975bf24fcbfc6843","tid":1135960,"uid":215924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":